title: Andromeda S01xE01-S02xE05 Blu-ray Remux
description:
Here's Andromeda 01x01-02x05 more to follow as i get them

These are released as upscales so arnt the best but i suppose the best you will get

though im convinced these are upscaled from the dvd encodes
and not the orig source

Its untouched from the blu-ray apart from the audio
there's no way i could ever justify a pcm audio track
on such an old release
